caller_intent: Armando is informing Rachel about a client (Larry Madlock) who mentioned a 30-year deadline for vehicle inspections, seeking clarification on whether the client's vehicle (model 93) required inspection.
resolution_steps: Armando explains Larry Madlock called to share a DMV-mentioned 30-year inspection rule.
Rachel clarifies that vehicles over 30 years old are exempt from inspection, referencing DMV website confirmation.
Armando confirms Larry Madlock already found the same information online and does not need further action.
summary: Armando relays a client's inquiry about a 30-year vehicle inspection deadline. Rachel confirms via DMV that vehicles over 30 years are exempt from inspection. The client already found this information online, so no further action is required.
